title: Coconut Muffins
ingredients: ['200g plain flour', '75g desiccated coconut', '100g caster sugar', '30g chopped toasted almonds', '1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '3/4 teaspoon grated orange zest', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '175ml coconut milk', '4 tablespoons orange juice', '4 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract']
